Outsource Programing Work Online: 
  A company/individual need to outsource coding effort, with clear requirements, e.g. unit test, deadline. 
  A programmer see that quest and finish it and provide the files, unit test results, demo to apply for reward.
  
Handy work:
  A house pipe is broken, they need a plumber to fix it, created a quest.
  A plumber accept and fixed it, he got a sign off/video/photo, he got paid by token.
  
Courier:
  Delivery this document form A to B, signed off correctly, and recieve token.

Put the money where your month is: 
  Bet against each order on his/her ability to lose weight, e.g. John bet Paul cannot loss 2 kg by next month.
  Paul believe he can and bet against John for some token, both place same amount, by when by what measures, the winner will take all.  
  Paul upload photo/video, and Simon is to decide if Paul achieved it.

Set goals for self/Others improvement:
  Parent provide rewards for their kids on acadamic/others achievements, reward is granted by teacher/anothers.
  Coach provide rewards for their clients, rewards is granted by measureable.
  Ones set goals for oneself to achieve, reward is granted by another, there is no cheating.

My Will be done:
  A will is set for the son to achieve certain goals (e.g. finish a bachelor degree, or get merry, or reach certain age) 
  before token is distributed to the son. Reward is granted by a custodian.
  
If you cought me, if I cought you.
  If someone cought me smoking in video, I will give him/her some token
